var book = {
	"name": "1 Timothy",
	"numChapters": 6,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>Paul, an apostle of Christ Jesus by the command of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29698A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29698A\"></sup> our Savior<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29698B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29698B\"></sup> and of Christ Jesus our hope,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29698C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29698C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>To Timothy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29699D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29699D\"></sup> my true son<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29699E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29699E\"></sup> in the faith:Grace, mercy and peace from God the Father and Christ Jesus our Lord.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29699F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29699F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>As I urged you when I went into Macedonia,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29700G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29700G\"></sup> stay there in Ephesus<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29700H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29700H\"></sup> so that you may command certain people not to teach false doctrines<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29700I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29700I\"></sup> any longer",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>or to devote themselves to myths<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29701J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29701J\"></sup> and endless genealogies.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29701K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29701K\"></sup> Such things promote controversial speculations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29701L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29701L\"></sup> rather than advancing God’s work—which is by faith.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The goal of this command is love, which comes from a pure heart<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29702M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29702M\"></sup> and a good conscience<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29702N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29702N\"></sup> and a sincere faith.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29702O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29702O\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Some have departed from these and have turned to meaningless talk.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>They want to be teachers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29704P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29704P\"></sup> of the law, but they do not know what they are talking about or what they so confidently affirm.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29704Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29704Q\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>We know that the law is good<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29705R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29705R\"></sup> if one uses it properly.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>We also know that the law is made not for the righteous<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29706S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29706S\"></sup> but for lawbreakers and rebels,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29706T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29706T\"></sup> the ungodly and sinful, the unholy and irreligious, for those who kill their fathers or mothers, for murderers,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>for the sexually immoral, for those practicing homosexuality, for slave traders and liars and perjurers—and for whatever else is contrary to the sound doctrine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29707U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29707U\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>that conforms to the gospel concerning the glory of the blessed God, which he entrusted to me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29708V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29708V\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I thank Christ Jesus our Lord, who has given me strength,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29709W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29709W\"></sup> that he considered me trustworthy, appointing me to his service.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29709X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29709X\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Even though I was once a blasphemer and a persecutor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29710Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29710Y\"></sup> and a violent man, I was shown mercy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29710Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29710Z\"></sup> because I acted in ignorance and unbelief.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29710AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29710AA\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The grace of our Lord was poured out on me abundantly,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29711AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29711AB\"></sup> along with the faith and love that are in Christ Jesus.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29711AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29711AC\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Here is a trustworthy saying<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29712AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29712AD\"></sup> that deserves full acceptance: Christ Jesus came into the world to save sinners<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29712AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29712AE\"></sup>—of whom I am the worst.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But for that very reason I was shown mercy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29713AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29713AF\"></sup> so that in me, the worst of sinners, Christ Jesus might display his immense patience<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29713AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29713AG\"></sup> as an example for those who would believe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29713AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29713AH\"></sup> in him and receive eternal life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29713AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29713AI\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Now to the King<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29714AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29714AJ\"></sup> eternal, immortal,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29714AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29714AK\"></sup> invisible,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29714AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29714AL\"></sup> the only God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29714AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29714AM\"></sup> be honor and glory for ever and ever. Amen.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29714AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29714AN\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Timothy, my son,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29715AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29715AO\"></sup> I am giving you this command in keeping with the prophecies once made about you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29715AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29715AP\"></sup> so that by recalling them you may fight the battle well,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29715AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29715AQ\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>holding on to faith and a good conscience,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29716AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29716AR\"></sup> which some have rejected and so have suffered shipwreck with regard to the faith.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29716AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29716AS\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Among them are Hymenaeus<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29717AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29717AT\"></sup> and Alexander,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29717AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29717AU\"></sup> whom I have handed over to Satan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29717AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29717AV\"></sup> to be taught not to blaspheme."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>I urge, then, first of all, that petitions, prayers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29718A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29718A\"></sup> intercession and thanksgiving be made for all people—",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>for kings and all those in authority,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29719B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29719B\"></sup> that we may live peaceful and quiet lives in all godliness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29719C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29719C\"></sup> and holiness.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>This is good, and pleases<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29720D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29720D\"></sup> God our Savior,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29720E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29720E\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>who wants<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29721F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29721F\"></sup> all people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29721G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29721G\"></sup> to be saved<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29721H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29721H\"></sup> and to come to a knowledge of the truth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29721I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29721I\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For there is one God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29722J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29722J\"></sup> and one mediator<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29722K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29722K\"></sup> between God and mankind, the man Christ Jesus,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29722L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29722L\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>who gave himself as a ransom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29723M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29723M\"></sup> for all people. This has now been witnessed to<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29723N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29723N\"></sup> at the proper time.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29723O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29723O\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And for this purpose I was appointed a herald and an apostle—I am telling the truth, I am not lying<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29724P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29724P\"></sup>—and a true and faithful teacher<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29724Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29724Q\"></sup> of the Gentiles.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29724R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29724R\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Therefore I want the men everywhere to pray, lifting up holy hands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29725S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29725S\"></sup> without anger or disputing.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I also want the women to dress modestly, with decency and propriety, adorning themselves, not with elaborate hairstyles or gold or pearls or expensive clothes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29726T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29726T\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>but with good deeds,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29727U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29727U\"></sup> appropriate for women who profess to worship God.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>A woman should learn in quietness and full submission.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29728V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29728V\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I do not permit a woman to teach or to assume authority over a man; she must be quiet.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29729W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29729W\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For Adam was formed first, then Eve.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29730X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29730X\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And Adam was not the one deceived; it was the woman who was deceived and became a sinner.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29731Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29731Y\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But women will be saved through childbearing—if they continue in faith, love<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29732Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29732Z\"></sup> and holiness with propriety."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>Here is a trustworthy saying:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29733A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29733A\"></sup> Whoever aspires to be an overseer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29733B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29733B\"></sup> desires a noble task.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Now the overseer is to be above reproach,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29734C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29734C\"></sup> faithful to his wife,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29734D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29734D\"></sup> temperate,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29734E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29734E\"></sup> self-controlled, respectable, hospitable,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29734F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29734F\"></sup> able to teach,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29734G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29734G\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>not given to drunkenness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29735H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29735H\"></sup> not violent but gentle, not quarrelsome,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29735I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29735I\"></sup> not a lover of money.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29735J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29735J\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>He must manage his own family well and see that his children obey him, and he must do so in a manner worthy of full respect.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29736K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29736K\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>(If anyone does not know how to manage his own family, how can he take care of God’s church?)<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29737L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29737L\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>He must not be a recent convert, or he may become conceited<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29738M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29738M\"></sup> and fall under the same judgment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29738N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29738N\"></sup> as the devil.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He must also have a good reputation with outsiders,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29739O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29739O\"></sup> so that he will not fall into disgrace and into the devil’s trap.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29739P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29739P\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>In the same way, deacons<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29740Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29740Q\"></sup> are to be worthy of respect, sincere, not indulging in much wine,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29740R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29740R\"></sup> and not pursuing dishonest gain.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>They must keep hold of the deep truths of the faith with a clear conscience.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29741S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29741S\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They must first be tested;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29742T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29742T\"></sup> and then if there is nothing against them, let them serve as deacons.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>In the same way, the women are to be worthy of respect, not malicious talkers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29743U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29743U\"></sup> but temperate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29743V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29743V\"></sup> and trustworthy in everything.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>A deacon must be faithful to his wife<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29744W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29744W\"></sup> and must manage his children and his household well.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29744X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29744X\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Those who have served well gain an excellent standing and great assurance in their faith in Christ Jesus.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Although I hope to come to you soon, I am writing you these instructions so that,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>if I am delayed, you will know how people ought to conduct themselves in God’s household, which is the church<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29747Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29747Y\"></sup> of the living God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29747Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29747Z\"></sup> the pillar and foundation of the truth.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Beyond all question, the mystery<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29748AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29748AA\"></sup> from which true godliness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29748AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29748AB\"></sup> springs is great:He appeared in the flesh,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29748AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29748AC\"></sup>was vindicated by the Spirit,was seen by angels,was preached among the nations,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29748AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29748AD\"></sup>was believed on in the world,was taken up in glory.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29748AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29748AE\"></sup>"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>The Spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29749A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29749A\"></sup> clearly says that in later times<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29749B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29749B\"></sup> some will abandon the faith and follow deceiving spirits<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29749C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29749C\"></sup> and things taught by demons.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Such teachings come through hypocritical liars, whose consciences have been seared as with a hot iron.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29750D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29750D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>They forbid people to marry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29751E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29751E\"></sup> and order them to abstain from certain foods,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29751F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29751F\"></sup> which God created<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29751G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29751G\"></sup> to be received with thanksgiving<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29751H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29751H\"></sup> by those who believe and who know the truth.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For everything God created is good,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29752I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29752I\"></sup> and nothing is to be rejected<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29752J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29752J\"></sup> if it is received with thanksgiving,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>because it is consecrated by the word of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29753K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29753K\"></sup> and prayer.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>If you point these things out to the brothers and sisters, you will be a good minister of Christ Jesus, nourished on the truths of the faith<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29754L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29754L\"></sup> and of the good teaching that you have followed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29754M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29754M\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Have nothing to do with godless myths and old wives’ tales;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29755N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29755N\"></sup> rather, train yourself to be godly.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29755O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29755O\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For physical training is of some value, but godliness has value for all things,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29756P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29756P\"></sup> holding promise for both the present life<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29756Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29756Q\"></sup> and the life to come.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29756R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29756R\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>This is a trustworthy saying<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29757S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29757S\"></sup> that deserves full acceptance.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>That is why we labor and strive, because we have put our hope in the living God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29758T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29758T\"></sup> who is the Savior of all people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29758U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29758U\"></sup> and especially of those who believe.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Command and teach these things.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29759V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29759V\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Don’t let anyone look down on you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29760W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29760W\"></sup> because you are young, but set an example<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29760X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29760X\"></sup> for the believers in speech, in conduct, in love, in faith<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29760Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29760Y\"></sup> and in purity.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Until I come,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29761Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29761Z\"></sup> devote yourself to the public reading of Scripture,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29761AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29761AA\"></sup> to preaching and to teaching.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Do not neglect your gift, which was given you through prophecy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29762AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29762AB\"></sup> when the body of elders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29762AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29762AC\"></sup> laid their hands on you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29762AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29762AD\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Be diligent in these matters; give yourself wholly to them, so that everyone may see your progress.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Watch your life and doctrine closely. Persevere in them, because if you do, you will save<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29764AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29764AE\"></sup> both yourself and your hearers."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>Do not rebuke an older man<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29765A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29765A\"></sup> harshly,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29765B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29765B\"></sup> but exhort him as if he were your father. Treat younger men<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29765C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29765C\"></sup> as brothers,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>older women as mothers, and younger women as sisters, with absolute purity.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Give proper recognition to those widows who are really in need.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29767D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29767D\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But if a widow has children or grandchildren, these should learn first of all to put their religion into practice by caring for their own family and so repaying their parents and grandparents,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29768E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29768E\"></sup> for this is pleasing to God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29768F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29768F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The widow who is really in need<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29769G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29769G\"></sup> and left all alone puts her hope in God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29769H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29769H\"></sup> and continues night and day to pray<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29769I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29769I\"></sup> and to ask God for help.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But the widow who lives for pleasure is dead even while she lives.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29770J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29770J\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Give the people these instructions,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29771K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29771K\"></sup> so that no one may be open to blame.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Anyone who does not provide for their relatives, and especially for their own household, has denied<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29772L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29772L\"></sup> the faith and is worse than an unbeliever.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>No widow may be put on the list of widows unless she is over sixty, has been faithful to her husband,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and is well known for her good deeds,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29774M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29774M\"></sup> such as bringing up children, showing hospitality,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29774N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29774N\"></sup> washing the feet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29774O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29774O\"></sup> of the Lord’s people, helping those in trouble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29774P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29774P\"></sup> and devoting herself to all kinds of good deeds.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>As for younger widows, do not put them on such a list. For when their sensual desires overcome their dedication to Christ, they want to marry.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Thus they bring judgment on themselves, because they have broken their first pledge.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Besides, they get into the habit of being idle and going about from house to house. And not only do they become idlers, but also busybodies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29777Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29777Q\"></sup> who talk nonsense,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29777R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29777R\"></sup> saying things they ought not to.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>So I counsel younger widows to marry,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29778S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29778S\"></sup> to have children, to manage their homes and to give the enemy no opportunity for slander.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29778T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29778T\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Some have in fact already turned away to follow Satan.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29779U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29779U\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>If any woman who is a believer has widows in her care, she should continue to help them and not let the church be burdened with them, so that the church can help those widows who are really in need.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29780V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29780V\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The elders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29781W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29781W\"></sup> who direct the affairs of the church well are worthy of double honor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29781X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29781X\"></sup> especially those whose work is preaching and teaching.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For Scripture says, “Do not muzzle an ox while it is treading out the grain,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29782Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29782Y\"></sup> and “The worker deserves his wages.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29782Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29782Z\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Do not entertain an accusation against an elder<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29783AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29783AA\"></sup> unless it is brought by two or three witnesses.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29783AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29783AB\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But those elders who are sinning you are to reprove<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29784AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29784AC\"></sup> before everyone, so that the others may take warning.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29784AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29784AD\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I charge you, in the sight of God and Christ Jesus<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29785AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29785AE\"></sup> and the elect angels, to keep these instructions without partiality, and to do nothing out of favoritism.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Do not be hasty in the laying on of hands,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29786AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29786AF\"></sup> and do not share in the sins of others.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29786AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29786AG\"></sup> Keep yourself pure.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29786AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29786AH\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Stop drinking only water, and use a little wine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29787AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29787AI\"></sup> because of your stomach and your frequent illnesses.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The sins of some are obvious, reaching the place of judgment ahead of them; the sins of others trail behind them.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>In the same way, good deeds are obvious, and even those that are not obvious cannot remain hidden forever."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>All who are under the yoke of slavery should consider their masters worthy of full respect,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29790A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29790A\"></sup> so that God’s name and our teaching may not be slandered.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29790B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29790B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Those who have believing masters should not show them disrespect just because they are fellow believers.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29791C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29791C\"></sup> Instead, they should serve them even better because their masters are dear to them as fellow believers and are devoted to the welfare of their slaves.These are the things you are to teach and insist on.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29791D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29791D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>If anyone teaches otherwise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29792E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29792E\"></sup> and does not agree to the sound instruction<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29792F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29792F\"></sup> of our Lord Jesus Christ and to godly teaching,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>they are conceited<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29793G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29793G\"></sup> and understand nothing. They have an unhealthy interest in controversies and quarrels about words<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29793H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29793H\"></sup> that result in envy, strife, malicious talk, evil suspicions",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>and constant friction between people of corrupt mind, who have been robbed of the truth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29794I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29794I\"></sup> and who think that godliness is a means to financial gain.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But godliness with contentment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29795J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29795J\"></sup> is great gain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29795K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29795K\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For we brought nothing into the world, and we can take nothing out of it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29796L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29796L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But if we have food and clothing, we will be content with that.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29797M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29797M\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Those who want to get rich<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29798N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29798N\"></sup> fall into temptation and a trap<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29798O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29798O\"></sup> and into many foolish and harmful desires that plunge people into ruin and destruction.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For the love of money<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29799P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29799P\"></sup> is a root of all kinds of evil. Some people, eager for money, have wandered from the faith<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29799Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29799Q\"></sup> and pierced themselves with many griefs.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29799R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29799R\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But you, man of God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29800S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29800S\"></sup> flee from all this, and pursue righteousness, godliness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29800T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29800T\"></sup> faith, love,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29800U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29800U\"></sup> endurance and gentleness.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Fight the good fight<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29801V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29801V\"></sup> of the faith. Take hold of<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29801W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29801W\"></sup> the eternal life<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29801X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29801X\"></sup> to which you were called when you made your good confession<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29801Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29801Y\"></sup> in the presence of many witnesses.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>In the sight of God, who gives life to everything, and of Christ Jesus, who while testifying before Pontius Pilate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29802Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29802Z\"></sup> made the good confession,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29802AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29802AA\"></sup> I charge you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29802AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29802AB\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>to keep this command without spot or blame<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29803AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29803AC\"></sup> until the appearing of our Lord Jesus Christ,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29803AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29803AD\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>which God will bring about in his own time<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29804AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29804AE\"></sup>—God, the blessed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29804AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29804AF\"></sup> and only Ruler,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29804AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29804AG\"></sup> the King of kings and Lord of lords,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29804AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29804AH\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>who alone is immortal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29805AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29805AI\"></sup> and who lives in unapproachable light,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29805AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29805AJ\"></sup> whom no one has seen or can see.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29805AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29805AK\"></sup> To him be honor and might forever. Amen.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29805AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29805AL\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Command those who are rich<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29806AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29806AM\"></sup> in this present world not to be arrogant nor to put their hope in wealth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29806AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29806AN\"></sup> which is so uncertain, but to put their hope in God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29806AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29806AO\"></sup> who richly provides us with everything for our enjoyment.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29806AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29806AP\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Command them to do good, to be rich in good deeds,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29807AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29807AQ\"></sup> and to be generous and willing to share.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29807AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29807AR\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>In this way they will lay up treasure for themselves<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29808AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29808AS\"></sup> as a firm foundation for the coming age, so that they may take hold of<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29808AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29808AT\"></sup> the life that is truly life.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Timothy, guard what has been entrusted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29809AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29809AU\"></sup> to your care. Turn away from godless chatter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29809AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29809AV\"></sup> and the opposing ideas of what is falsely called knowledge,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>which some have professed and in so doing have departed from the faith.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29810AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29810AW\"></sup>Grace be with you all.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29810AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29810AX\"></sup>"
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;